---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About Onyx Labs"
  description="Learn about Onyx Labs, an AI consultancy helping teams ship responsible, production-grade AI systems."
>
  <section class="content-main">
    <div class="container shell">
      <div class="content-layout">
        <div>
          <h1 class="content-heading">An AI partner that ships with you.</h1>
          <p class="content-lede">
            Onyx Labs exists for teams who want the leverage of AI without losing control of risk,
            reliability, or user trust.
          </p>
          <div class="content-tags">
            <span class="tag">AI Governance</span>
            <span class="tag">Product & Engineering</span>
            <span class="tag">Hands-on Delivery</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="content-panel">
          <h3>How we work</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>We work in small, senior teams.</li>
            <li>We ship real systems, not just slide decks.</li>
            <li>We collaborate directly with your builders.</li>
            <li>We leave you with capability, not dependency.</li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </div>

      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="content-panel">
          <h3>Principles</h3>
          <p>
            We believe in pairing ambitious AI work with clear-eyed pragmatism. That means
            prioritizing safety, usability, and maintainability alongside innovation.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Start from the problem, not the model.</li>
            <li>Design for human control and oversight.</li>
            <li>Measure what matters in production.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="content-panel">
          <h3>Who we partner with</h3>
          <p>
            We primarily work with product companies, SaaS platforms, and internal platform teams
            who are ready to invest seriously in AI capabilities.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Early-stage teams validating their first AI features.</li>
            <li>Growth-stage companies scaling AI across products.</li>
            <li>Enterprises formalizing AI governance and platforms.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-section">
        <div class="section-header">
          <div>
            <div class="section-title">What makes us different</div>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
              Governance, training, consulting, and development all under one roof — with a bias
              toward shipping.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-label">Integrated</div>
            <div class="card-title">End-to-end AI expertise</div>
            <p class="card-body-text">
              We combine governance, product, and engineering experience so you don't have to
              coordinate multiple vendors.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-label">Hands-on</div>
            <div class="card-title">Builders, not only advisors</div>
            <p class="card-body-text">
              We are as comfortable in your codebase and dashboards as we are in strategy and
              policy reviews.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-label">Pragmatic</div>
            <div class="card-title">Clear trade-offs, no hype</div>
            <p class="card-body-text">
              You get grounded recommendations with trade-offs explained in plain language, not
              buzzwords.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
